♪Wrong, wrong, wrong♪

9
00:01:19,530 --> 00:01:20,120
[Si Jin]

10
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:23,930
[Adapted from Si Jin,
by Dong Tian De Liu Ye]

11
00:01:23,940 --> 00:01:27,950
[Episode 13]

12
00:01:32,610 --> 00:01:33,490
I'll take it back

13
00:01:34,009 --> 00:01:34,729
and tend to it with care.

14
00:01:35,450 --> 00:01:36,970
Whenever you wish to receive it,

15
00:01:37,410 --> 00:01:38,130
I'll bring it over.

16
00:01:40,370 --> 00:01:41,090
I shall take my leave.

17
00:01:56,780 --> 00:01:57,740
Mr. Yu!

18
00:02:04,620 --> 00:02:06,580
Eavesdropping and spying
are not the actions of a gentleman.

19
00:02:07,220 --> 00:02:08,860
This is already the second time
you've done this.

20
00:02:10,900 --> 00:02:11,780
I never claimed

21
00:02:11,780 --> 00:02:13,540
to be a gentleman in the first place.

22
00:02:19,980 --> 00:02:20,700
My apologies.

23
00:02:21,780 --> 00:02:23,440
I thought

24
00:02:23,540 --> 00:02:24,900
you were fond of Mr. Zhen.

25
00:02:27,140 --> 00:02:27,380
I...

26
00:02:27,810 --> 00:02:28,690
Who I favor is none

27
00:02:29,540 --> 00:02:30,650
of your business.

28
00:02:31,180 --> 00:02:32,380
Of course, it is!

29
00:02:32,780 --> 00:02:33,220
Must you

30
00:02:33,220 --> 00:02:34,620
be so distant with me?

31
00:02:34,710 --> 00:02:35,670
Aren't we…?

32
00:02:37,540 --> 00:02:38,020
Aren't we what?

33
00:02:41,210 --> 00:02:41,850
Neighbors?

34
00:02:44,510 --> 00:02:45,750
You must be joking.

35
00:02:46,540 --> 00:02:48,380
The begonia I sent
as a housewarming gift

36
00:02:48,579 --> 00:02:49,780
was returned.

37
00:02:50,410 --> 00:02:52,290
Clearly, I was overestimating myself
in thinking I could be close

38
00:02:52,310 --> 00:02:53,710
to such a distinguished neighbor.

39
00:02:56,010 --> 00:02:56,930
It was returned?

40
00:02:57,410 --> 00:02:58,210
I never sent it back!

41
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:01,020
It must have been Long Dan.

42
00:03:01,910 --> 00:03:02,790
That fool

43
00:03:02,830 --> 00:03:04,230
who only ever ruins things.

44
00:03:08,810 --> 00:03:09,930
The soil has some issues.

45
00:03:10,410 --> 00:03:13,410
I wanted to trouble you
to take a look at it.

46
00:03:14,210 --> 00:03:14,970
What's wrong with the soil?

47
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:15,380
The soil…

48
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:16,120
Yu!

49
00:03:16,810 --> 00:03:18,050
I can't hit the target!

50
00:03:18,579 --> 00:03:19,860
Is my bow broken?

51
00:03:19,980 --> 00:03:21,340
Come take a look at it!

52
00:03:22,380 --> 00:03:23,260
Long Dan!

53
00:03:23,540 --> 00:03:24,740
Take a look at it!

54
00:03:24,860 --> 00:03:25,300
Yes, sir.

55
00:03:33,700 --> 00:03:36,180
The soil is a bit loose.

56
00:03:37,380 --> 00:03:37,900
Really?

57
00:03:37,980 --> 00:03:38,460
Yes.

58
00:03:39,420 --> 00:03:40,220
You'll know when you see it.

59
00:03:41,980 --> 00:03:43,140
Why didn't you say something earlier?

60
00:03:43,180 --> 00:03:44,579
I wasn't given a chance to.

61
00:03:46,579 --> 00:03:49,460
Today wasn't my day off.

62
00:03:50,540 --> 00:03:52,540
I took time off
to teach Jiang Zhan archery and riding,

63
00:03:53,310 --> 00:03:54,630
and to ask

64
00:03:55,010 --> 00:03:56,610
if you were troubled by something.

65
00:04:02,210 --> 00:04:04,290
You dreamed that Jiang Zhan would die?

66
00:04:05,980 --> 00:04:07,340
But dreams aren't real.

67
00:04:08,110 --> 00:04:09,190
What if it becomes real?

68
00:04:09,910 --> 00:04:11,510
That dream felt so vivid.

69
00:04:12,190 --> 00:04:13,310
I saw him fall into the water.

70
00:04:13,790 --> 00:04:15,350
I saw the restaurant engulfed in flames.

71
00:04:15,780 --> 00:04:16,940
And I saw a memorial tablet
with my brother's name on it

72
00:04:17,310 --> 00:04:18,750
added to our ancestral hall.

73
00:04:19,990 --> 00:04:21,430
If Zhan really might die,

74
00:04:22,210 --> 00:04:23,330
I have to prevent it.

75
00:04:24,640 --> 00:04:25,640
I hit the target!

76
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,120
Yu! Si!

77
00:04:27,310 --> 00:04:28,830
Look! I hit it!

78
00:04:29,310 --> 00:04:30,430
Come over and see!

79
00:04:30,550 --> 00:04:31,790
Just look at Jiang Zhan.

80
00:04:32,550 --> 00:04:33,510
If you keep him locked up

81
00:04:33,750 --> 00:04:34,909
at home every day,

82
00:04:35,190 --> 00:04:36,230
it will only backfire.

83
00:04:36,710 --> 00:04:38,590
He'll find every excuse to sneak out.

84
00:04:39,350 --> 00:04:40,230
Instead of that,

85
00:04:40,870 --> 00:04:42,310
why don't we take turns accompanying him

86
00:04:42,790 --> 00:04:44,430
whenever he goes out?

87
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:45,560
What do you think?

88
00:04:46,810 --> 00:04:47,890
You don't think what I'm saying

89
00:04:47,890 --> 00:04:48,610
is ludicrous?

90
00:04:49,170 --> 00:04:50,250
I know you care about him.

91
00:04:54,450 --> 00:04:56,330
Miss Si really said that?

92
00:04:57,690 --> 00:04:58,250
Yes.

93
00:04:59,290 --> 00:05:01,810
I've already told her.

94
00:05:02,740 --> 00:05:05,100
We'll put aside
talks of marriage for now.

95
00:05:06,210 --> 00:05:07,290
Oh, you!

96
00:05:07,490 --> 00:05:08,650
A bride already within reach,

97
00:05:08,690 --> 00:05:09,770
and you let her slip away!

98
00:05:10,010 --> 00:05:12,330
Mother, we should

99
00:05:12,810 --> 00:05:13,490
respect

100
00:05:13,490 --> 00:05:14,490
Miss Si's wishes.

101
00:05:17,450 --> 00:05:19,890
So be it. I was too impatient.

102
00:05:20,690 --> 00:05:22,810
She was set up

103
00:05:23,090 --> 00:05:24,130
at Madam Jiang's birthday banquet.

104
00:05:24,330 --> 00:05:26,890
I knew the Count of Dongping's Mansion

105
00:05:27,210 --> 00:05:28,570
was a place filled
with schemes and plots.

106
00:05:28,850 --> 00:05:30,490
I was hasty and made a rash decision,

107
00:05:30,970 --> 00:05:31,930
thinking that if I could get her

108
00:05:32,050 --> 00:05:33,450
into our family sooner,

109
00:05:33,570 --> 00:05:34,610
she would suffer less.

110
00:05:35,650 --> 00:05:36,690
Looking back,

111
00:05:38,730 --> 00:05:40,530
I shouldn't force her.

112
00:05:45,130 --> 00:05:46,490
Everything you did is for me.

113
00:05:47,290 --> 00:05:48,490
What's your plan now?

114
00:05:48,850 --> 00:05:50,930
Just give up on this marriage?

115
00:05:56,530 --> 00:05:57,890
Recognize one's shortcomings,
then improve.

116
00:05:58,610 --> 00:05:59,930
Aim for the peak,
then strive to reach it.

117
00:06:01,210 --> 00:06:02,850
I shall not give up

118
00:06:05,210 --> 00:06:07,170
so long as Miss Si does not
give her hand to another.

119
00:06:08,290 --> 00:06:08,970
Good.

120
00:06:53,880 --> 00:07:00,780
[Yesterday is gone like autumn leaves.
Tomorrow is long and full of hope.]

121
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:14,800
♪A sudden glance,
just like our first meeting♪

122
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:18,320
♪Feelings remain,
but things are ever unclear♪

123
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:21,640
♪Memories replay♪

124
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:25,240
♪My heart hesitates♪

125
00:07:25,910 --> 00:07:26,930
♪Can I make it through
another long night?♪

126
00:07:27,310 --> 00:07:27,830
Chief.

127
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:29,230
How much are you writing?

128
00:07:29,960 --> 00:07:31,230
♪Afraid of losing you again♪

129
00:07:31,230 --> 00:07:32,110
Is this big enough for you?

130
00:07:32,710 --> 00:07:34,430
Keep… Keep going.

131
00:07:34,430 --> 00:07:36,720
♪The pain lingers deep inside♪

132
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:40,080
♪Leaving dreams incomplete♪

133
00:07:40,350 --> 00:07:44,350
Yesterday is gone like autumn leaves.

134
00:07:45,390 --> 00:07:49,150
Tomorrow is long and full of hope.

135
00:07:49,150 --> 00:07:53,840
♪Past lives fade like smoke,
can the dreams be undone?♪

136
00:07:54,610 --> 00:07:58,010
♪I still can't let you go♪

137
00:07:58,450 --> 00:08:01,570
♪No matter how far the journey takes me♪

138
00:08:01,910 --> 00:08:05,490
♪If love is strong,
what is there to fear?♪

139
00:08:05,630 --> 00:08:06,840
♪In this lifetime♪

140
00:08:07,110 --> 00:08:10,440
Can all our troubles really be solved?

141
00:08:16,510 --> 00:08:19,800
♪Can I make it through
another long night?♪

142
00:08:20,140 --> 00:08:23,220
♪Afraid of losing you again♪

143
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:26,890
♪The pain lingers deep inside♪

144
00:08:27,180 --> 00:08:30,260
♪Leaving dreams incomplete♪

145
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:34,240
♪I count the petals as they fall♪

146
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:37,970
♪Each one a time I've thought of you♪

147
00:08:38,299 --> 00:08:45,220
♪Past lives fade like smoke,
can the dreams be undone?♪

148
00:08:45,260 --> 00:08:48,680
♪I still can't let you go♪

149
00:08:49,050 --> 00:08:52,170
♪No matter how far the journey takes me♪

150
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:56,010
♪I'll do anything to save♪

151
00:08:56,260 --> 00:09:02,800
♪Our shared past♪

152
00:09:13,540 --> 00:09:14,140
Please take another look!

153
00:09:14,740 --> 00:09:15,460
[Lushengxiang Store]
Half-price for a limited time!

154
00:09:15,820 --> 00:09:17,020
Madam, please have a look.

155
00:09:17,060 --> 00:09:17,820
We're offering a limited-time discount.

156
00:09:18,100 --> 00:09:18,540
Madam.

157
00:09:18,660 --> 00:09:19,260
Half-price at Lushengxiang Store.

158
00:09:19,300 --> 00:09:20,300
Would you like to go inside?

159
00:09:20,740 --> 00:09:21,260
Half-price for a limited time.

160
00:09:21,260 --> 00:09:22,500
Would you like to take a look?
Buy something for your wife!

161
00:09:22,580 --> 00:09:22,860
No.

162
00:09:22,900 --> 00:09:23,780
Half-price at Lushengxiang Store.

163
00:09:23,780 --> 00:09:25,380
Greetings. Come inside and take a look.

164
00:09:25,580 --> 00:09:26,460
Our products smell exquisite.

165
00:09:26,740 --> 00:09:28,260
Only half price for a limited time.
Check it out!

166
00:09:28,300 --> 00:09:28,820
No.

167
00:09:28,820 --> 00:09:29,940
Miss. Come on.

168
00:09:29,940 --> 00:09:31,780
[Lushengxiang Store]

169
00:09:31,810 --> 00:09:32,930
The shop was finally renovated,

170
00:09:33,170 --> 00:09:34,410
but business has plummeted.

171
00:09:34,640 --> 00:09:36,210
We've gotten no customers
for days in a row.

172
00:09:37,110 --> 00:09:38,230
Even our regular patrons

173
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:39,360
have been returning their purchases.

174
00:09:39,810 --> 00:09:41,290
When I asked them privately,

175
00:09:41,490 --> 00:09:43,210
they said that a certain noble person
had spread the word.

176
00:09:43,640 --> 00:09:45,240
Anyone who dares to buy
from the Lushengxiang Store

177
00:09:45,310 --> 00:09:46,350
would be making an enemy of her.

178
00:09:46,910 --> 00:09:48,150
They wouldn't say

179
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:49,000
who the noble is.

180
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,160
If it's someone of that importance,

181
00:09:50,510 --> 00:09:51,190
then it's definitely not

182
00:09:51,190 --> 00:09:52,230
the work of our business rivals.

183
00:09:53,510 --> 00:09:55,030
Perhaps we've offended someone.

184
00:09:55,410 --> 00:09:56,580
Several of our regulars

185
00:09:56,640 --> 00:09:57,410
are family members

186
00:09:57,410 --> 00:09:58,690
of high-ranking officials.

187
00:09:59,510 --> 00:10:00,630
For someone to intimidate them

188
00:10:00,630 --> 00:10:01,590
into staying away,

189
00:10:01,980 --> 00:10:03,380
who could it be?

190
00:10:04,540 --> 00:10:05,380
I'll ask Miss Si.

191
00:10:05,580 --> 00:10:06,060
Wait here.

192
00:10:06,510 --> 00:10:08,430
Miss, come inside
and look at our fragrance dew.

193
00:10:09,950 --> 00:10:10,910
Miss Si and Mr. Zhan.

194
00:10:10,910 --> 00:10:11,750
What do we do?

195
00:10:11,750 --> 00:10:13,310
No one is willing
to step foot inside our store.

196
00:10:14,470 --> 00:10:15,550
Everyone, stay calm.

197
00:10:15,990 --> 00:10:16,750
Commandant Yu is already

198
00:10:16,750 --> 00:10:17,550
investigating the matter.

199
00:10:18,270 --> 00:10:19,030
As they say,

200
00:10:19,110 --> 00:10:20,230
good things are worth waiting for.

201
00:10:20,710 --> 00:10:21,350
I refuse to believe

202
00:10:21,350 --> 00:10:22,510
that anyone has the power

203
00:10:22,750 --> 00:10:23,350
to stop every single patron

204
00:10:23,350 --> 00:10:24,350
from coming to us.

205
00:10:24,590 --> 00:10:25,310
Si is right.

206
00:10:26,390 --> 00:10:27,390
I know some friends.

207
00:10:27,590 --> 00:10:28,950
I'll treat them to a few drinks

208
00:10:29,030 --> 00:10:29,670
and ask them

209
00:10:29,710 --> 00:10:30,510
to introduce some customers to us.

210
00:10:30,710 --> 00:10:31,190
No.

211
00:10:31,950 --> 00:10:32,510
Why not?

212
00:10:33,030 --> 00:10:34,190
What use do you think

213
00:10:34,190 --> 00:10:35,190
your drinking buddies are?

214
00:10:35,470 --> 00:10:36,550
Are you just looking for an excuse

215
00:10:36,710 --> 00:10:37,910
to go out and make merry again?

216
00:10:38,070 --> 00:10:39,270
Do you seriously think

217
00:10:39,270 --> 00:10:40,070
I'd be in the mood

218
00:10:40,110 --> 00:10:41,030
to fool around right now?

219
00:10:41,350 --> 00:10:42,750
How could you think that of me?

220
00:10:48,350 --> 00:10:49,070
All right.

221
00:10:49,630 --> 00:10:50,710
The bottom line is

222
00:10:50,710 --> 00:10:51,870
that you are not going to them.

223
00:10:52,830 --> 00:10:53,470
Fine.

224
00:11:06,970 --> 00:11:12,590
[Lushengxiang Store]

225
00:11:16,210 --> 00:11:17,650
Oh, you give me such a good laugh.

226
00:11:18,340 --> 00:11:20,500
All right. That's enough.

227
00:11:20,780 --> 00:11:22,020
Don't let the fun get you down.

228
00:11:22,740 --> 00:11:24,100
This is the first time I've ever heard

229
00:11:24,140 --> 00:11:24,940
of a younger sister

230
00:11:25,020 --> 00:11:26,420
keeping her older brother at home,

231
00:11:26,500 --> 00:11:27,740
not allowing him to step out at all.

232
00:11:27,780 --> 00:11:28,620
What do you know?

233
00:11:29,020 --> 00:11:30,700
My sister is doing it for my own good.

234
00:11:31,020 --> 00:11:32,700
[Zhang Sheng]
She wants me to fool around less

235
00:11:33,020 --> 00:11:34,380
and work harder to improve myself.

236
00:11:34,780 --> 00:11:35,260
All right.

237
00:11:36,260 --> 00:11:37,220
I'll be on my way now.

238
00:11:37,380 --> 00:11:38,180
Wouldn't want to interrupt
your self-improvement.

239
00:11:38,380 --> 00:11:39,660
Wait, no! Don't go!

240
00:11:39,820 --> 00:11:40,940
Come back!

241
00:11:42,540 --> 00:11:43,420
You have no idea

242
00:11:43,660 --> 00:11:45,580
how boring it is to drink alone.

243
00:11:46,060 --> 00:11:47,460
A grown man

244
00:11:47,660 --> 00:11:48,860
so obedient to his sister.

245
00:11:49,380 --> 00:11:50,500
Wouldn't it be embarrassing
if word gets out?

246
00:11:50,740 --> 00:11:51,380
So what?

247
00:11:52,300 --> 00:11:53,180
My sister is

248
00:11:53,220 --> 00:11:54,220
way smarter than me.

249
00:11:54,380 --> 00:11:56,140
Can't go wrong with her judgment.

250
00:11:56,780 --> 00:11:59,140
The more obedient you are,

251
00:11:59,420 --> 00:12:00,660
the less she'll respect you.

252
00:12:00,700 --> 00:12:02,540
My sister would never look down on me.

253
00:12:04,220 --> 00:12:04,580
I suppose?

254
00:12:07,980 --> 00:12:09,340
She's your sister.

255
00:12:09,540 --> 00:12:10,980
Would she tell you that to your face?

256
00:12:11,540 --> 00:12:12,780
What use do you think

257
00:12:12,780 --> 00:12:13,780
your drinking buddies are?

258
00:12:13,940 --> 00:12:15,100
Are you just looking for an excuse

259
00:12:15,220 --> 00:12:16,500
to go out and make merry again?

260
00:12:19,060 --> 00:12:20,260
If I pass

261
00:12:20,660 --> 00:12:21,580
the Imperial Insignia Guard selection,

262
00:12:21,940 --> 00:12:23,420
she will change her opinion of me.

263
00:12:23,660 --> 00:12:24,860
She'll never think I'm useless again.

264
00:12:24,980 --> 00:12:26,500
And if you fail?

265
00:12:29,580 --> 00:12:30,060
What?

266
00:12:31,340 --> 00:12:32,700
Are you certain you'll pass?

267
00:12:42,060 --> 00:12:43,220
Not at all.

268
00:12:44,540 --> 00:12:46,260
Zhang, you know me.

269
00:12:46,580 --> 00:12:47,860
With my flashy but useless skills,

270
00:12:47,980 --> 00:12:49,500
no matter how hard I practice,

271
00:12:49,900 --> 00:12:51,540
I still feel uncertain.

272
00:12:52,020 --> 00:12:52,940
These women.

273
00:12:52,940 --> 00:12:53,940
I don't get what they're thinking.

274
00:12:54,780 --> 00:12:55,700
Why do they always expect

275
00:12:55,700 --> 00:12:57,060
a man to have an official title

276
00:12:57,100 --> 00:12:58,060
to be considered successful?

277
00:12:58,500 --> 00:13:00,340
What's so great about being
an Imperial Insignia Guard anyway?

278
00:13:01,300 --> 00:13:02,900
Harsh conditions
and hard work every day.

279
00:13:03,860 --> 00:13:04,940
True.

280
00:13:12,700 --> 00:13:14,980
Have you no other way

281
00:13:15,780 --> 00:13:17,860
to impress your sister?

282
00:13:24,180 --> 00:13:24,660
Zhang.

