286
00:13:35,020 --> 00:13:35,980
I do.

287
00:13:36,340 --> 00:13:37,940
Really? That's great!

288
00:13:39,100 --> 00:13:39,540
Here.

289
00:13:39,620 --> 00:13:40,140
Here.

290
00:13:52,300 --> 00:13:52,660
Ji.

291
00:13:53,780 --> 00:13:54,860
Jiang Zhan took the bait?

292
00:13:55,780 --> 00:13:56,500
Of course.

293
00:13:59,980 --> 00:14:01,500
Get the job done,

294
00:14:01,780 --> 00:14:02,580
and Her Highness promises

295
00:14:02,820 --> 00:14:04,660
that there will be a position
in the Office of Ceremonies for you.

296
00:14:05,580 --> 00:14:07,900
I will not disappoint Her Highness.

297
00:14:09,060 --> 00:14:09,540
I bid you farewell.

298
00:14:30,180 --> 00:14:30,780
Zhang.

299
00:14:31,340 --> 00:14:33,020
This buyer of yours,

300
00:14:33,020 --> 00:14:34,980
she's not some courtesan, is she?

301
00:14:35,220 --> 00:14:36,660
What does it matter who she is?

302
00:14:36,660 --> 00:14:37,780
What matters is that she's rich.

303
00:14:38,020 --> 00:14:39,860
Anyway, tonight's lady

304
00:14:39,900 --> 00:14:41,740
is extremely generous.

305
00:14:41,940 --> 00:14:43,220
If you can close this deal,

306
00:14:43,420 --> 00:14:44,900
Lushengxiang Store won't have to worry

307
00:14:44,900 --> 00:14:45,700
about business for an entire year.

308
00:14:46,980 --> 00:14:47,700
Promise me

309
00:14:48,140 --> 00:14:48,940
you won't get on a boat

310
00:14:49,180 --> 00:14:50,300
or go near the river!

311
00:14:51,780 --> 00:14:53,820
It's just a boat ride!

312
00:14:54,940 --> 00:14:56,100
Maybe I should just forget it.

313
00:14:56,180 --> 00:14:57,220
If my sister finds out

314
00:14:57,220 --> 00:14:58,340
I came to a place like this,

315
00:14:58,500 --> 00:14:59,340
she'll never let me live it down.

316
00:14:59,820 --> 00:15:01,420
You're always talking about your sister.

317
00:15:01,620 --> 00:15:02,980
Can you even live without her?

318
00:15:03,020 --> 00:15:03,820
What do you mean by that?

319
00:15:04,100 --> 00:15:05,380
Of course, I can live

320
00:15:05,420 --> 00:15:05,940
without her!

321
00:15:06,420 --> 00:15:07,380
Is that so? Prove it.

322
00:15:08,020 --> 00:15:08,940
Come on. Let's go.

323
00:15:09,060 --> 00:15:10,620
Slow… Slow down.

324
00:15:11,540 --> 00:15:12,060
Come on.

325
00:15:13,980 --> 00:15:14,780
Here.

326
00:15:15,220 --> 00:15:16,340
Fill his cup.

327
00:15:16,900 --> 00:15:17,660
I'm not drinking.

328
00:15:18,300 --> 00:15:19,500
Drink.

329
00:15:25,300 --> 00:15:26,220
Let me help you.

330
00:15:26,460 --> 00:15:27,540
- Come on.
- Zhang.

331
00:15:46,240 --> 00:15:47,200
I must have the wrong place.

332
00:15:57,410 --> 00:15:58,050
Leave us.

333
00:16:09,050 --> 00:16:10,210
I had no idea
that Your Highness was here

334
00:16:10,210 --> 00:16:11,570
with the company.

335
00:16:12,050 --> 00:16:12,970
My friend

336
00:16:13,090 --> 00:16:13,850
took a wrong turn.

337
00:16:14,170 --> 00:16:15,330
We've disturbed your gathering.

338
00:16:15,650 --> 00:16:17,130
Apologies.

339
00:16:17,580 --> 00:16:18,340
Wait.

340
00:16:19,340 --> 00:16:22,100
It was us who told your friend

341
00:16:22,260 --> 00:16:23,380
to bring you here.

342
00:16:30,180 --> 00:16:32,340
Your Highness, what do you mean?

343
00:16:32,620 --> 00:16:35,460
Weren't you curious
about who's been disrupting

344
00:16:35,460 --> 00:16:37,220
Lushengxiang Store's business?

345
00:16:37,610 --> 00:16:38,730
I shall answer you.

346
00:16:39,250 --> 00:16:40,530
It was me.

347
00:16:43,450 --> 00:16:44,210
Impossible!

348
00:16:44,770 --> 00:16:47,570
Everyone knows
that Your Highness is kind and virtuous!

349
00:16:47,930 --> 00:16:49,050
You would never do such a thing!

350
00:16:49,210 --> 00:16:50,450
This… This must be my fault.

351
00:16:51,210 --> 00:16:52,090
I've always had a bad habit

352
00:16:52,210 --> 00:16:53,650
of running my mouth.

353
00:16:53,810 --> 00:16:55,330
Everyone here knows that.

354
00:16:55,530 --> 00:16:57,450
I must have offended

355
00:16:57,450 --> 00:16:58,410
Your Highness somewhere.

356
00:16:58,610 --> 00:17:00,890
I humbly ask you to enlighten me.

357
00:17:02,240 --> 00:17:03,840
You're quite the clever one.

358
00:17:04,980 --> 00:17:05,540
Very well.

359
00:17:06,579 --> 00:17:08,380
I'm in a good mood today.

360
00:17:08,710 --> 00:17:10,510
I'll be gracious

361
00:17:11,030 --> 00:17:12,069
and let this slide.

362
00:17:13,030 --> 00:17:14,150
Thank you, Your Highness.

363
00:17:20,990 --> 00:17:22,430
I didn't say you could leave.

364
00:17:24,210 --> 00:17:25,010
