370
00:17:33,710 --> 00:17:35,510
Someone, bring Jiang some liquor.

371
00:17:35,990 --> 00:17:36,430
I…

372
00:17:43,790 --> 00:17:44,710
Your Highness…

373
00:17:44,870 --> 00:17:46,750
Finish these three jars,

374
00:17:47,470 --> 00:17:49,430
and I will leave
Lushengxiang Store alone.

375
00:17:50,070 --> 00:17:50,510
What do you say?

376
00:17:52,210 --> 00:17:52,640
It...

377
00:17:55,190 --> 00:17:55,950
Your Highness.

378
00:17:57,670 --> 00:17:58,550
Do you mean it?

379
00:17:58,750 --> 00:17:59,550
Of course.

380
00:18:07,630 --> 00:18:09,670
I thank Your Highness
for your generosity.

381
00:18:17,390 --> 00:18:18,470
