386
00:18:29,990 --> 00:18:30,710
What's your problem?

387
00:18:31,070 --> 00:18:32,950
Her Highness has granted you

388
00:18:33,230 --> 00:18:34,350
such precious liquor,

389
00:18:34,950 --> 00:18:35,950
