Enough.

416
00:20:15,790 --> 00:20:16,350
Hold him down.

417
00:20:18,510 --> 00:20:20,430
You spilled earlier.

418
00:20:21,310 --> 00:20:24,110
Take it easy this time.

419
00:20:25,710 --> 00:20:28,270
There's no hurry.

420
00:20:29,910 --> 00:20:30,550
Jiang Zhan!

421
00:20:31,630 --> 00:20:33,070
Mr. Jiang!

422
00:20:33,870 --> 00:20:34,750
Jiang Zhan!

423
00:20:36,990 --> 00:20:37,510
How was that?

424
00:20:39,030 --> 00:20:39,710
Speak!

425
00:20:42,270 --> 00:20:42,790
What?

426
00:20:44,030 --> 00:20:45,030
Kill me.

427
00:20:46,830 --> 00:20:47,310
Kill you?

428
00:20:49,190 --> 00:20:50,070
