out of his misery.

429
00:20:51,910 --> 00:20:52,710
That's a first

430
00:20:52,790 --> 00:20:54,190
for me!

431
00:21:01,550 --> 00:21:03,230
Drink up. Take your time.

432
00:21:15,550 --> 00:21:16,350
Breathe!

433
00:21:19,150 --> 00:21:20,190
Don't play dead.

434
00:21:22,110 --> 00:21:22,710
Ji.

435
00:21:23,190 --> 00:21:24,310
Is he…?

436
00:21:25,270 --> 00:21:25,910
Jiang Zhan.

437
00:21:32,790 --> 00:21:33,270
Jiang Zhan?

438
00:21:34,350 --> 00:21:34,950
Zhan!

439
00:21:37,590 --> 00:21:38,070
Zhan!

440
00:21:39,070 --> 00:21:39,950
What are you doing?

441
00:21:40,030 --> 00:21:40,670
I'm not your brother.

442
00:21:40,670 --> 00:21:41,710
Excuse me.

443
00:21:43,190 --> 00:21:43,950
Zhan!

444
00:21:49,840 --> 00:21:50,440
Oh, no.

445
00:21:50,750 --> 00:21:52,110
He… He has stopped breathing!

446
00:21:52,310 --> 00:21:53,230
He's too weak.

447
00:21:53,310 --> 00:21:54,190
He's dead! What…?

448
00:21:54,390 --> 00:21:55,630
What do we do, Your Highness?

449
00:21:58,350 --> 00:21:59,310
Strip him.

450
00:22:04,510 --> 00:22:05,190
Sorry.

451
00:22:33,940 --> 00:22:34,610
Zhan.

452
00:22:40,780 --> 00:22:41,340
Are you all right?

453
00:22:44,540 --> 00:22:45,260
Your Highness.

454
00:22:47,310 --> 00:22:48,590
He's really dead.

455
00:22:51,590 --> 00:22:52,230
Boring.

456
00:22:52,950 --> 00:22:53,590
What do we do?

457
00:22:56,380 --> 00:22:59,020
What's the big deal?
It's just a worthless life.

458
00:22:59,310 --> 00:23:00,110
Even if he's useless,

459
00:23:00,610 --> 00:23:02,210
he's still an heir to the count.

460
00:23:06,210 --> 00:23:07,610
Then let's just throw him into the river

461
00:23:08,290 --> 00:23:09,450
