462
00:23:11,770 --> 00:23:12,290
Someone.

463
00:23:13,130 --> 00:23:13,570
Throw him in the river.

464
00:23:23,690 --> 00:23:24,410
Jiang Zhan!

465
00:23:24,610 --> 00:23:25,050
Not bad.

466
00:23:28,170 --> 00:23:29,770
Look! Someone fell into the water!

467
00:23:30,050 --> 00:23:30,930
What happened?

468
00:23:31,050 --> 00:23:32,170
Probably drank too much.

469
00:23:36,040 --> 00:23:38,310
Wake up, Zhan!

470
00:23:58,580 --> 00:23:59,110
He fell into the water!

471
00:23:59,140 --> 00:23:59,940
Someone fell into the water!

472
00:24:01,710 --> 00:24:02,670
Mingyue!

473
00:24:03,510 --> 00:24:04,950
What are we going to do

474
00:24:05,110 --> 00:24:06,270
if Uncle learns about this?

475
00:24:09,010 --> 00:24:10,410
Then have them get rid

476
00:24:10,410 --> 00:24:11,730
of these servants.

477
00:24:12,530 --> 00:24:13,570
By tomorrow,

478
00:24:13,570 --> 00:24:14,450
I don't want to see them in Ling'an City

479
00:24:14,450 --> 00:24:15,530
ever again.

480
00:24:16,510 --> 00:24:18,110
- No!
- No!

481
00:24:18,770 --> 00:24:20,290
Your Highness! Mercy!

482
00:24:21,410 --> 00:24:21,850
Move it.

483
00:24:22,890 --> 00:24:23,290
Move!

484
00:24:24,510 --> 00:24:24,910
Hurry up!

485
00:24:37,180 --> 00:24:39,940
For what happened
with Jiang Zhan tonight,

486
00:24:39,940 --> 00:24:41,180
everyone present shall be

487
00:24:41,660 --> 00:24:44,260
