488
00:24:44,260 --> 00:24:46,780
- Thank you, Your Highness!
- I appreciate it, Your Highness!

489
00:24:49,010 --> 00:24:49,690
Zhang Sheng.

490
00:24:50,010 --> 00:24:52,090
You are today's biggest contributor.

491
00:24:52,170 --> 00:24:54,050
You brought Jiang Zhan here.

492
00:24:54,050 --> 00:24:54,610
A big buyer

493
00:24:55,540 --> 00:24:58,380
of fragrance dew, huh?

494
00:24:59,140 --> 00:25:00,540
The fact

495
00:25:01,020 --> 00:25:03,060
that he actually believed it
is hilarious!

496
00:25:04,140 --> 00:25:04,910
I'm flattered.

497
00:25:05,100 --> 00:25:06,820
It was Ji's idea.

498
00:25:06,940 --> 00:25:07,980
Ji gets the credit.

499
00:25:07,980 --> 00:25:09,100
- Ji.
- Yes.

500
00:25:09,310 --> 00:25:10,590
Ji.

501
00:25:10,740 --> 00:25:11,340
Oh, stop it!

502
00:25:11,340 --> 00:25:12,020
You can handle it.

503
00:25:12,380 --> 00:25:15,460
We're just here for a bit of fun,

504
00:25:15,460 --> 00:25:16,060
