had him stripped.

511
00:25:30,340 --> 00:25:31,140
Yes.

512
00:25:31,820 --> 00:25:34,580
Your Highness,
did you enjoy yourself tonight?

513
00:25:34,580 --> 00:25:35,340
No.

514
00:25:35,980 --> 00:25:38,060
Tell me. What's the difference
between a person

515
00:25:38,860 --> 00:25:40,220
and an ant?

516
00:25:40,340 --> 00:25:41,300
None.

517
00:25:41,740 --> 00:25:42,940
They both belong to Your Highness.

518
00:25:43,210 --> 00:25:44,650
I want

519
00:25:44,650 --> 00:25:46,010
Jiang Si dead.

520
00:25:47,610 --> 00:25:48,940
Cui Mingyue,

521
00:25:49,140 --> 00:25:50,540
I'll make you

522
00:25:50,910 --> 00:25:52,510
