523
00:26:29,240 --> 00:26:30,180
Jiang Zhan!

524
00:26:42,510 --> 00:26:43,310
Fire!

525
00:26:44,030 --> 00:26:44,750
Run!

526
00:26:45,310 --> 00:26:46,750
Run!

527
00:27:43,610 --> 00:27:44,370
Miss Jiang.

528
00:27:47,730 --> 00:27:48,650
Those animals.

529
00:27:49,530 --> 00:27:51,290
Yang Shengcai. Zhang Sheng.

530
00:27:52,250 --> 00:27:53,530
They tortured my brother

531
00:27:54,610 --> 00:27:56,090
to death

532
00:27:56,810 --> 00:27:57,970
and then threw him

533
00:27:57,970 --> 00:27:59,770
