534
00:28:08,600 --> 00:28:12,900
[Xiayue Pavilion]

535
00:28:14,210 --> 00:28:14,970
Remember.

536
00:28:15,690 --> 00:28:16,970
You were with me the entire night.

537
00:28:16,970 --> 00:28:18,170
You were nowhere else.

538
00:29:03,610 --> 00:29:04,090
Chief!

539
00:29:04,290 --> 00:29:05,330
