719
00:35:52,010 --> 00:35:53,050
It's too dangerous!

720
00:35:55,050 --> 00:35:56,170
Well? Did you find anything?

721
00:35:56,380 --> 00:35:56,940
No.

722
00:35:57,740 --> 00:35:58,140
Long Dan.

