00:36:09,940 --> 00:36:11,260
Come on! Let's help find him!

731
00:36:11,310 --> 00:36:12,180
Hurry！

732
00:36:12,240 --> 00:36:13,610
Over there!

733
00:36:13,810 --> 00:36:14,610
A thousand liang!

734
00:36:14,810 --> 00:36:15,510
A thousand liang!

