767
00:37:17,020 --> 00:37:17,780
Over there!

768
00:37:18,380 --> 00:37:19,060
Master!

769
00:37:20,100 --> 00:37:22,460
Hurry! Pull him up!

770
00:37:31,340 --> 00:37:32,380
A purple robe.

