836
00:41:56,980 --> 00:41:58,940
I cannot fathom how this wretch

837
00:41:59,580 --> 00:42:00,900
became entangled

838
00:42:00,900 --> 00:42:02,500
with Princess Mingyue.

839
00:42:08,220 --> 00:42:09,460
